namedLocations.description: A ZIP Code is a postal code used by the United States Postal Service (USPS) in a system it introduced in 1963. The term ZIP is an acronym for Zone Improvement Plan; it was chosen to suggest that the mail travels more efficiently and quickly (zipping along) when senders use the code in the postal address. The basic format consists of five digits. An extended ZIP+4 code was introduced in 1983 which includes the five digits of the ZIP Code, followed by a hyphen and four additional digits that reference a more specific location.

transcript.text: Hello, in this video we will learn about how to create store branding.
Let's talk about the key features and benefits.
Admin can add custom text, change the background color, add an image or a flash video in the background.
Custom theme colors options are available which allow you to change as per your requirement.
It allows you to personalize the store login page, registration page and reset password page.
Let's have a look into the admin.
Click on store management store, search for the store name you are looking for and click on action button.
Select configuration.
Here you can see we have given to change website logo where you can upload your site logo for website mobile, favicon, e-mail logo etcetera and then save it.
After that, the theme configuration allows you to change the theme.
Here we have given some standard themes like Sea blue, corporate sales theme etcetera.
Also, you can choose a custom theme with the color of your choice.
For example, if we choose orange color theme and save it, we will see the change in the storefront.
As you can see over here, it's changed to an orange color theme.
Similarly, you can make a different color theme as per your choice.
So it will change the theme color.
Also, you can choose a custom color.
You can choose and check in which area to apply the color from the help section given here.
Next, we have page personalization.
Here you can personalize your login page with a signup link.
For example copy the variable text, paste it over here and save it.
So you can see on the storefront the registration button appears over here.
Similarly on the registration page when customer click on registration button this also you can personalize as per your requirement using HTML source code or you can add some background images.
Similarly we have given reset password page personalization where you can reset the password over here.
This page also you can personalize also we have given a custom CSS portion where you can put your own custom CSS code for more changes in your storefront.
Thanks for watching this video.
Feel free to connect with us in case of any queries.
